---
import uniqueImage from "../assets/img/CUREO5/Patient-Therapeut-Happy1.jpg";
---

<section class="unique" data-reveal>
  <div class="unique-shell">
    <article class="unique-grid">
      <div class="unique-content">
        <p class="eyebrow">THERAPY IMPACT</p>
        <h2>What Makes Virtual Reality Therapy Unique?</h2>
        <p>
          VR therapy provides immersive training sessions that engage multiple
          senses at once. The combination of visual, auditory and physical
          stimuli activates targeted neurocognitive and motor functions.
        </p>
        <p>
          Compared to traditional methods, active participation is
          significantly increased, with proven effects on motivation, therapy
          adherence and treatment quality. Therapists remain in control of all
          processes via tablet.
        </p>
        <p>
          CUREO is based on three key principles for therapeutic success:
          gamification, virtual reality (VR), and embodiment. Gamification uses
          game-like elements to increase motivation and therapy adherence.
        </p>
        <p>
          Through targeted incentives such as points, progress indicators, and
          new challenges, therapy becomes an engaging and activating experience.
          This playful approach encourages repetition, helping to consolidate
          movement patterns and achieve lasting training results.
        </p>

        <div class="principles" aria-label="Core principles">
          <span>Gamification</span>
          <span>Virtual Reality</span>
          <span>Embodiment</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="unique-media">
        <img src={uniqueImage.src} alt="Therapist and patient using CUREO VR therapy" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .unique {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8fcf2 0%, #f3f9eb 100%);
    padding: 0 1.2rem 2rem;
  }

  .unique-shell {
    margin: 0 auto;
    max-width: 1240px;
  }

  .unique-grid {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 165, 59, 0.34);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(88, 126, 50, 0.1);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(340px, 1fr) minmax(320px, 1.05fr);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .unique-content {
    align-self: center;
    padding: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    color: #688247;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    margin: 0 0 0.55rem;
  }

  .unique-content h2 {
    color: #1d2f1d;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.7vw, 2.2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .unique-content p {
    color: #425641;
    line-height: 1.56;
    margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
  }

  .principles {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
  }

  .principles span {
    background: rgba(142, 188, 72, 0.13);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 165, 59, 0.45);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: #2f4a2d;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.36rem 0.72rem;
  }

  .unique-media {
    min-height: 420px;
  }

  .unique-media img {
    display: block;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    width: 100%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .unique-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .unique-media {
      max-height: 420px;
      min-height: 300px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .unique {
      padding: 0 0.8rem 1.6rem;
    }
  }
</style>
